osures, and elastic waistbands all add ease to your life?shopping at Amazon.com offers another convenience. Thanks to the wide selection of baby clothes from Amazon.com, snapping a little one into comfort is as easy as the click of a button.", "parent_text": "Toys, Kids, Baby", "keyword_density": {"baby clothes": "4.6", "baby": "3.6", "amazoncom": "1.3", "baby clothes from amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 118},
