owsable selection of everything from makeup, skin care, hair care, tools and accessories, perfume and cologne, and loads of top brands like Olay, L\u2019Oreal Paris, Covergirl, Pantene, Vidal Sassoon, Suave, Dove, Maybelline, Garnier, The Body Shop, Nivea, Eucerin, and many, many more. Plus, we offer email updates on all the latest trends, products, new brands, and exclusive offers, so you can shop from our page or from your email. Thanks to free shipping on eligible items sold and shipped by Amazon.com, you can give your wallet and your look an instant lift. When you shop the Beauty Products Store at Amazon.com, you can luxuriate in beautiful and bright color palettes, protect your skin with clinical-strength lotions, and stay ready for anything with your arsenal of beauty tools. Get ready for a must-have look that\u2019s all your own.", "parent_text": "Beauty, Health, Grocery", "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "1.0", "beauty products": "3.1", "products": "1.8", "beauty": "2.6"}, "department_id": 105},
