{"department_text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "text": "Patio, Lawn & Garden", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Patio-Lawn-Garden/b/ref=sd_allcat_lp/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2972638011", "description_title": "Lawn Equipment from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"lawn equipment from amazoncom": 1, "lawn": 7, "lawn equipment": 5, "amazoncom": 4}, "description_wc": 313, "description_text": "No matter what the weather is like, your garden and lawn is a great place to relax and take a break from your busy life. Amazon.com carries all sort of lawn equipment to make sure that the time you spend in your front or back yard is as comfortable and inviting as possible. We have a wide variety of lawn equipment to help you with any landscaping and gardening chores. Mowers, trimmers and blowers can make keeping lawns neat and tidy, conveying an extremely welcoming and open environment. Useful watering tools, like heavy-duty hoses and spray nozzles are essential for making sure that all of your garden flowers and veggies get the moisture they need. We also have lawn equipment to help with your gardening, such as pruning shears, spades and germination trays. Once you\u2019ve polished and perfected your front and back yard, it\u2019s time to host a barbeque, and Amazon.com carries everything you need to throw a great outdoor party. You can find propane, natural gas, and charcoal burning grills easily among our outdoor cooking supplies. For serious eats, try special smokers and fryers built especially for outdoor use to give your barbeque unique and unforgettable flavor. We also have the tongs, spatulas, grill scrapers and other outdoor cooking accessories to make grilling fun. Take advantage of the selection of lawn equipment Amazon.com has to help you entertain for your outdoor party. Patio chairs, swinging benches and even hammocks can make it easy to relax and enjoy the peace of your garden. When it gets cold, we have many different styles of outdoor heaters to keep you and your guests warm and cozy. When it gets warmer outside, our pool supplies will help you cool down and keep you ready for a season of wet summer fun. Prepare for the changing seasons with the diverse lawn equipment from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden, Tools", "keyword_density": {"lawn equipment": "3.2", "lawn": "2.2", "lawn equipment from amazoncom": "1.3", "amazoncom": "1.3"}, "department_id": 94},
