{"department_text": "Home Improvement", "nr_products": 6558919, "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-and-Home-Improvement/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi2/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=228013", "text": "Home Improvement", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tools-and-Home-Improvement/b/ref=sd_allcat_hi2/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=228013", "description_title": "Tools & Home Improvement", "keyword_count": {"home": 6, "tools": 7, "home improvement": 3}, "description_wc": 372, "description_text": "Amazon.com's Tools and Home Improvement Store is an ideal spot for campers, carpenters, contractors, craft enthusiasts, electricians, home-owners, plumbers, tree-trimmers, woodworkers, and those who just want to restock or expand their tool collection or start some serious home repairs. If you've decided to remodel a living room or bathroom, for example, all the necessary fixtures are here, including ceiling fans, ENERGY STAR qualified lighting, lamps, light fixtures, recessed lighting, switches and outlets, and other illuminating items, as well as bathroom faucets, bathroom sinks, bidets, showerheads, toilets, toilet parts, water heaters, and water pumps. If your home repair involves becoming a bit more social there are door chimes and bells for any tastes, and as more people might be stopping by it's not a bad idea to stock up on paint, paint brushes, paint sprayers, solvents, stain, wall stickers and murals, and wallpaper. And to reach the right places, don\u2019t forget ladders and stepladders. Without the proper tools, however, it's probable that most projects aren't going to get done, or at least not be done well. Both tool newbies and hard-core contractors (and every tool collector in-between) can find the right hand tools and power tools here, helpful products such as drills, flashlights, routers, saws, and woodworking tools. To ensure the tools don\u2019t take over a room or garage, a tool organizer is a necessity. Once the project is done, don't forget to put on the finishing touches, the doorknobs and lock sets, garage doors, house numbers, mailboxes, and shelving. To make sure that your work stands strong and safe, remember to get fire safety products, other safety and security products, padlocks and hasps, safes, and security systems. No matter what home improvements or tool-related venture you're taking on, Amazon.com has the trustworthy brands delivering the helpful products you'll want, brands like 3M, Adesso, American Standard, Bosch, Bulbrite, Culligan, DEWALT, Dale Tiffany, Dremel, Elegant Lighting, Filtrete, Honeywell, InSinkErator, Kidde, Kohler, Kwikset, Leviton, Pfister, Roommates, and more. You'll also find a wide range of deals and special offers on tools and home improvement products in the Value Center. Now, all that's needed is deciding where to start.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden, Tools", "keyword_density": {"home": "1.6", "tools": "1.9", "home improvement": "1.6"}, "department_id": 99},
{"department_text": "Pet Supplies", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "text": "Pet Supplies", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/pet-supplies-dog-cat-food-bed-toy/b/ref=sd_allcat_ps/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2619533011", "description_title": "Pet Supplies from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"pet": 20, "pet supplies": 6, "pet supplies from amazoncom": 1, "supplies": 7}, "description_wc": 343, "description_text": "Puppies, rabbits, kittens, parrots, rodents, lizards, fish, and other pets all have one thing in common: their humans love them. If you\u2019re bringing home a new pet, or if you\u2019re browsing for something new for an old family friend, we have all the pet supplies you need to ensure your pet\u2019s health and longevity. We have all the pet supplies and food you could need to ensure your critter\u2019s health. If your new little family member eats pellets, kibble, flakes, or veggies, we have what they love. We carry pet food from some of the most trusted names in pet nutrition, including Purina, Kaytee, Fancy Feast, and much more. Nutrition for pets is just as important as it is for us humans; their attitude and energy levels can drastically improve when they\u2019re getting the right vitamins, minerals, and proteins they need. The next step is to ensure your pet\u2019s hygiene. We carry cage liners for a variety of small pets and birds. They\u2019re much easier to deal with than traditional shredded newspaper and sawdust options, because these pet supplies are built to be especially absorptive. We also have kitty litter for cats, training supplies for dogs, and a wide variety of filters for fish. Whether your pet scurries, swims or squawks, make sure they have a clean environment to thrive in. Once you\u2019ve taken care of all the necessary pet supplies, it\u2019s time to get down to the fun part. Pet toys can make spending time with your furry, scaly, or feathered friend even more enjoyable than it already is. There are a variety of toys to enrich caged pets, and there are also balls, climbing structures, and chew toys for larger animals. If you filter your search for pet supplies by price, you can see the most affordable pet toys first, so you can afford to treat your pet to some extra love. Live your life to the fullest, and ensure your pets can do the same with the pet supplies from Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Home, Garden, Tools", "keyword_density": {"pet": "5.8", "pet supplies": "3.5", "pet supplies from amazoncom": "1.2", "supplies": "2.0"}, "department_id": 97},
{"department_text": "Computer Parts & Components", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/PC-Parts-Components/b/ref=sd_allcat_components/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=193870011", "text": "Computer Parts & Components", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/PC-Parts-Components/b/ref=sd_allcat_components/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=193870011", "description_title": "Computer Parts and Components from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"amazoncom": 2, "computer parts": 5, "computer": 11, "components": 4, "computer parts and components": 1}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "If you\u2019re looking to repair, build, or upgrade your computer, you can find the components and computer parts you need at Amazon.com. We have a wide variety of computer parts and components, so whether you\u2019re trying to build a computer from the ground up or you just need to replace a few things for optimal performance, you can find what you need. Our hard disk drives and solid state drives come in a wide variety of capacities to hold all of your games, music, movies, and TV shows without a problem., and our high-performance sound cards and graphics cards can help you create the ultimate entertainment experience with crisp pictures and life-like sounds. For those who want to build their own tower, we carry the computer parts and hardware to get you started. We have a great selection of computer cases and chasses in metal or plastic, with USB 3.0 capabilities, windowed side panels, and amazing designs. We also have reliable and fast processors from some of the top manufacturers, including Intel, AMD, Corsair, Kingston, Crucial for Memory, and more. If you\u2019re shopping for computer parts on a budget, try filtering our processors, SSDs, or other components by price, by used or refurbished models, and even by discount to see some of the most affordable options available. For a faster computer experience, we carry many different memory modules to boost your RAM. Increasing your memory by one to 16 gigabytes can significantly improve your multitasking abilities so you can go between video chatting, playing games, listening to music and more without your computer getting bogged down by all the open applications. We even have an assortment of ergonomic, purpose-built, and other input devices to give you more control over your user interface. Find the components and computer parts you need to repair, build, or upgrade your computer at Amazon.com.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"amazoncom": "0.6", "computer parts": "3.2", "computer": "3.5", "components": "1.3", "computer parts and components": "1.3"}, "department_id": 85},
{"department_text": "Trade In Your Electronics", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Electronics-Trade-In/b/ref=sd_allcat_trade_in_elec/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2226766011", "text": "Trade In Your Electronics", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Electronics-Trade-In/b/ref=sd_allcat_trade_in_elec/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2226766011", "description_title": "Tell Us What You Think", "keyword_count": {"think": 1, "us": 2}, "description_wc": 30, "description_text": "We're always looking to improve the customer experience in the Electronics Trade-In Store and would love to hear your feedback. Please let us know what you think .", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"think": "3.4", "us": "6.9"}, "department_id": 81},
{"department_text": "Desktops & Monitors", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Desktops/b/ref=sd_allcat_deskserv/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=4972214011", "text": "Desktops & Monitors", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Desktops/b/ref=sd_allcat_deskserv/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=4972214011", "description_title": "Desktop Computers & Monitors at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"desktop computers": 4, "desktop": 5}, "description_wc": 268, "description_text": "Desktop computers are far from dead. Avid gamers, media professionals, or just home users looking for serious expandability all still look to desktop computers to suit their needs, and there are plenty of great machines available. Check out the best in desktop computers here at Amazon, from brands like Acer, Alienware, Apple, ASUS, CyberpowerPC, CybertronPC, Dell, Gateway, HP, iBUYPOWER, Lenovo, Sony, and Toshiba. You can check out our Desktop Buying Guide to find out a bit more about the right machine for you. Maybe you\u2019re looking for a newer all-in-one PC, where the monitor and CPU are a single unit, saving you all kinds of space in setting it up. Or maybe you\u2019re after the latest and greatest gaming PC--a good gaming PC is a cut above the average machine, with enhanced graphics, processing power, a supercharged cooling system, and other features to keep it at peak performance. Whether it\u2019s a gaming PC or any other type, you\u2019ll be covered here. Shop by price, brand, and other criteria such as desktop computers with a specific processor type (AMD or Intel). Check out best sellers, new releases, top rated and most gifted machines, and more. Once you\u2019ve picked out your machine you\u2019ll need to pick a monitor. Amazon has you covered there as well. Look for a monitor by size, check out monitor best sellers, choose between LCD and LED monitor types, and more. Whether you\u2019re after a massive high-definition monitor (for that gaming PC rig) or something a bit more modest, you\u2019ll find it here.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"desktop computers": "3.0", "desktop": "1.9"}, "department_id": 83},
{"department_text": "Electronics Accessories", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tech-Accessories-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_elec_acc/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=5745855011", "text": "Electronics Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Tech-Accessories-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_elec_acc/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=5745855011", "description_title": "Welcome to the Consumer Electronics Accessory Store at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"consumer electronics accessory store": 1, "electronics accessory": 3, "electronics": 5, "amazoncom": 1, "accessory": 4}, "description_wc": 158, "description_text": "Amazon\u2019s Consumer Electronics Accessory Store is your one-stop shop for all your electronics accessories needs. Don\u2019t know what electronics accessory or peripheral you\u2019re looking for? We are here to help. Check out our accessories in the Computers, Tablets, Office, Cameras, Cell Phones, GPS, Audio & Video, MP3, Car Electronics, or Kindle categories and find your perfect accessory. With our huge selection of cables, adapters, batteries, chargers, cases, bags, covers, sleeves, stands, mounts, power protection, ink, toner, and headsets from popular brands like HP, Canon, Belkin, OtterBox, Monster, Sony, Brother, Logitech, Apple, Sennheiser, Bose, and more, we have something for every electronic and gadget buyer. Whether your budget is limited or not, we consistently work toward maintaining competitive prices on every electronics accessory we carry. And with customer benefits such as Amazon Prime and FREE Super Saver Shipping , you can shop with confidence at Amazon.com, as we strive to give you the best customer experience.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"consumer electronics accessory store": "2.5", "electronics accessory": "3.8", "amazoncom": "0.6", "electronics": "3.2", "accessory": "2.5"}, "department_id": 80},
{"department_text": " Laptops & Tablets", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Laptops-Tablets/b/ref=sd_allcat_lapnet/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2956501011", "text": " Laptops & Tablets", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Laptops-Tablets/b/ref=sd_allcat_lapnet/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2956501011", "description_title": "Laptops, Ultrabooks & Tablets at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {}, "description_wc": 328, "description_text": "Nowadays, it\u2019s all about portability. More and more of us have left behind the bulky desktop PC for these smaller, more mobile (and these days just as powerful) counterparts. Still haven\u2019t made the leap? Amazon is the perfect one-stop shop for a new laptop, tablet, or Ultrabook. With brands like Acer, Apple, ASUS, Dell, HP, Kindle Fire HD, Lenovo, Samsung, Sony, and Toshiba, you\u2019re sure to end up with a great machine. On the laptop front, you\u2019ll find all the standard styles, whether you\u2019re looking for a PC, Mac, Chromebook, Netbook, touchscreen laptop, Ultrabook, or more. Check out laptop best sellers, peruse our best deals, check out our helpful buying guides, and more\u2014you\u2019ll find just the right laptop model for you. If you\u2019re looking for a powerful, ultra-portable laptop, an Ultrabook may be just the right choice. An Ultrabook is a high-end subnotebook, outfitted with a low-power Intel processor, solid-state drive, and other technologies to give you a featherweight form-factor without losing performance or battery life. If you\u2019re unsure of which Ultrabook would suit your needs, our Ultrabook Buying Guide might be a good place to start. Or perhaps you\u2019re after a tablet? Tablet computing is increasingly popular, and it\u2019s no wonder why. These flat, touchscreen devices let you casually surf the web, enjoy music and video, play games, download and use apps (tablet speak for applications), read eBooks, and so much more. Our Tablet Buying Guide can help you find the right tablet for your needs, or you can check out best sellers, browse by brand, and more to do your research. You can also check out our selection of 2-in-1, aka convertible, machines, which combine a tablet and laptop in one. So whether you\u2019re looking for a laptop, Ultrabook, or tablet\u2014or even some combination of the above\u2014you\u2019ve come to the right place.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {}, "department_id": 82},
