{"department_text": "Video Games", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "text": "Video Games", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/computer-video-games-hardware-accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_cvg/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=468642", "description_title": "Video Games from Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"video": 6, "amazoncom": 3, "video games": 5, "games": 9}, "description_wc": 227, "description_text": "Amazon\u2019s Video Games store is your entertainment hub for everything related to Video Games. The store features thousands of games at great prices and allows you to shop by gaming platform, bestsellers, new and future releases, bonus offers, price, deals, genre, ESRB rating, and more. You can shop for every type of game you may be looking for, including Xbox 360 , PlayStation 3 , PlayStation 4 , Nintendo Wii and Wii U, Nintendo 3DS, PlayStation Vita, Digital, Free-to-Play, Kindle Fire, PC and Mac, Nintendo DS, and much more. When you\u2019re looking to join in on the hottest new video game developments online, there\u2019s no better place to be than Amazon.com. Our new & future releases section features the latest games and newest pre-order options. Its streamlined, hassle-free pages are perfect for locating new video games in seconds, so you\u2019ll be at the forefront of all the action and right in line with even the most hardcore gaming aficionados. No matter which gaming system you use, Amazon.com offers the latest updates and releases on new video games. For bonus offers and everyday savings on a wide selection of games and accessories, visit our Deals Store . Don\u2019t forget to trade in the games you\u2019ve already finished for Amazon.com gift cards in the Video Games Trade-In Store .", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"games": "4.1", "amazoncom": "1.4", "video games": "4.5", "video": "2.7"}, "department_id": 76},
{"department_text": "Camera, Photo & Video", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Camera-Photo-Film-Canon-Sony/b/ref=sd_allcat_p/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=502394", "text": "Camera, Photo & Video", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Camera-Photo-Film-Canon-Sony/b/ref=sd_allcat_p/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=502394", "description_title": "Camera, Photo & Video", "keyword_count": {"photo": 5, "camera photo video": 1, "camera": 15}, "description_wc": 283, "description_text": "Amazon.com has a huge selection of cameras and accessories for every type of photographer. Looking for a pocket-sized camera for those unforgettable moments? Amazon.com has a huge selection of cameras small enough to keep with you everywhere you go. If you are looking for something in the professional realm, Amazon.com has a wide selection of the newest and most precise Digital SLR cameras with all the lenses and accessories to help you get that perfect image. Looking for something in between? Our broad range of compact system cameras has everything you need to start building your digital portfolio. From the smallest, most agile point & shoot digital cameras to the professional level Digital SLR cameras, Amazon.com's Camera, Photo & Video store has something for everyone. We feature the newest models from the biggest brands in photography such as Canon, Nikon, Panasonic, Sony, Olympus, and Panasonic. We not only have the base camera models, but also a plethora of lenses and accessories for every situation. If you are looking for a specialty camera, Amazon has a variety of underwater and kid\u2019s cameras as well. Our selection of underwater cameras has everything for the most hard core scuba divers as well as the cautiously clumsy. These can help you capture those incredible underwater photos or just keep your camera safe at the beach. Our children\u2019s cameras come in a variety of themes and colors and are an excellent way to inspire kids to show the unique way they see their world. All of this comes with the largest selection of reviews with the lowest prices around. So find that perfect camera for you or the perfect gift for the photographers closest to you.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"photo": "1.8", "camera photo video": "1.1", "camera": "5.3"}, "department_id": 74},
{"department_text": "Computer Accessories & Peripherals", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Computer-Accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_compaccess/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2956536011", "text": "Computer Accessories & Peripherals", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Computer-Accessories/b/ref=sd_allcat_compaccess/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2956536011", "description_title": "Computer Accessories at Amazon.com", "keyword_count": {"computer": 6, "accessories": 7, "computer accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 241, "description_text": "Looking for an external hard drive to expand your storage, a router to set up your own network, or just a more comfortable keyboard and mouse? Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store has all these and more. You\u2019re sure to find what you need in our broad selection of computer accessories and peripherals, including flash memory cards and USB drives, wired and wireless PC headsets, cables, and laptop bags, batteries, and cases. Check out our best sellers, top-rated computer accessories, and helpful customer reviews. We have accessories for every need and every computer, Mac or PC, from compact, high-speed SDHC and microSD flash memory cards to full-featured peripherals like wired and wireless keyboards, mice, headsets, and microphones designed for business, gaming, and home computing. If you\u2019re tough on your devices, don\u2019t miss our selection of rugged and spill-resistant accessories. Does your home or office network need a boost? Take a look at our selection of AC and N Wi-Fi routers. If it\u2019s deals you want, look no further. We have big discounts on every kind of computer accessory. Or maybe you just need more cables for all your gadgets. We\u2019ll keep you connected and in sync with USB, Ethernet, SATA, Lightning cables and more. If you\u2019re always on the go, protect and power your laptop and accessories with our bags, cases, batteries, and chargers--all in Amazon\u2019s Computer Accessories Store.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"computer": "2.5", "accessories": "2.9", "computer accessories": "3.3"}, "department_id": 84},
