{"department_text": "Home Audio & Theater", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "text": "Home Audio & Theater", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/Home-Audio-Electronics/b/ref=sd_allcat_hat/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=667846011", "description_title": "Home Audio and Home Theater", "keyword_count": {"home audio": 3, "home theater": 1, "audio": 6, "theater": 6, "home": 12}, "description_wc": 312, "description_text": "Entertaining friends and family can be a lot of work. Whether you are hosting a movie night and want a cinema-quality sound system or just easy listening at home, you will find everything you need right here. At Amazon.com's Home Audio and Theater Store we have an unbeatable selection of home entertainment brands, a list that includes top brands such as Sonos, Polk Audio, Bose, Yamaha, Logitech, Onkyo, Soundmatters International, Eton, Definitive Technology, Pyle, ZVOX, MartinLogan, C. Crane Company, Marantz, Midland Consumer Radio, Audio-Technica, Coby, Crosley Radio, Sony, Samsung, Panasonic, Grace Digital, Bic America, LG, Denon, JBL, Sangean, Infinity, Klipsch, Harman Kardon, Vizio, Pioneer, Energy, Boston Acoustics, Atlantic Technology, RCA, and more. These brands have become trusted over time because of their expertise in a wide variety of home entertainment products. Within this long list of brands, you'll be able to find home entertainment products for all your needs, starting with the essential speakers for any home. Our store carries bookshelf speakers, subwoofers, floorstanding speakers, center channel speakers, ceiling speakers, wireless speakers, soundbars, indoor speakers, outdoor speakers, and a variety of home theater system speaker sets. We also carry a variety of other products that complete your home entertainment system such as receivers, amplifiers, CD players, CD recorders, turntables, and more. If you're building a movie theater in your own home, you'll want to be sure you have the proper components to replicate the theater experience: projectors, surround speaker systems, receivers, and amplifiers. You can also find everything you need to listen on-the-go in our store. We carry boomboxes, portable radios, clock radios, and compact stereos that make it easy to take audio anywhere. Need help finding the right home audio and theater products? Our featured home audio and theater categories make it easy to find the perfect addition to your home entertainment system.", "parent_text": "Electronics, Computers", "keyword_density": {"home audio": "1.9", "home theater": "0.6", "audio": "1.9", "theater": "1.9", "home": "3.8"}, "department_id": 73},
{"department_text": "Movies & TV", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/movies-tv-dvd-bluray/b/ref=sd_allcat_mov/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2625373011", "text": "Movies & TV", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/movies-tv-dvd-bluray/b/ref=sd_allcat_mov/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2625373011", "description_title": "More About Movies & TV at Amazon", "keyword_count": {"tv": 6, "movies": 3, "amazon": 2, "movies tv": 2}, "description_wc": 164, "description_text": "The Amazon Movies & TV Store is your one stop shop for films and TV shows--new releases, best sellers, and today's best deals. With over 500,000 DVDs and Blu-rays to choose from, you\u2019ll find plenty of favorites right here. Search for exactly what you\u2019re looking for or discover new DVD and Blu-ray titles by browsing the Movies & TV Store. You can shop by genre, format, price, and more, or check out editors\u2019 picks for a curated selection. Shop our Deals Store for daily movie and TV deals on DVD and Blu-ray, as well as our TV and Blu-ray Deal of the Week. Finally, if you\u2019re looking for new movies or TV shows, check out the New Release store. When you pre-order select DVDs or Blu-rays at Amazon you get our Pre-order Price Guarantee. Also, you can receive your order on release date with our Release-Date Delivery program (restrictions apply). Happy Shopping!", "parent_text": "Movies, Music, Games", "keyword_density": {"tv": "3.7", "movies": "1.8", "amazon": "1.2", "movies tv": "2.5"}, "department_id": 62},
