{"department_text": "Audible Audiobooks & More", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_aud_bks/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2402172011", "text": "Audible Audiobooks & More", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/b/ref=sd_allcat_aud_bks/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2402172011", "description_title": "About Audible Audiobooks", "keyword_count": {"audible": 5, "audiobooks": 6}, "description_wc": 177, "description_text": "Audible.com is the Internet's leading provider of digital audiobooks, featuring more than 150,000 titles available for download. These titles include books, magazines, radio shows, podcasts, stand-up comedy, and speeches. We feature the best narrators interpreting bestselling books by top authors. Audible's audiobooks can be downloaded to over 500+ mp3 players, including Kindle\u2122 and iPod\u00ae. You can also download and listen to audiobooks on MP3 players from Creative, Zune, and other top manufacturers. And with Audible's new apps for iPhone\u2122 and Android\u2122, you can now download and listen to audiobooks wirelessly on your phone. The best way to experience Audible is as a member. Members choose a listening plan that suits their pace, and enjoy access to exclusive sales, promotions, and discounts. Members also receive monthly credits good for the audiobook of their choice, plus 30% off all audiobooks purchased without credits. So, if you'd like to enjoy more books, more often, experience books in a whole new way with digital audiobooks from Audible.com that you can listen to anytime, anywhere.", "parent_text": "Books, Audible", "keyword_density": {"audible": "2.9", "audiobooks": "3.4"}, "department_id": 60},
{"department_text": "Blu-ray", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.amazon.com/movies-tv-bluray-bluray3d/b/ref=sd_allcat_blu/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2901953011", "text": "Blu-ray", "department_url": "http://www.amazon.com/movies-tv-bluray-bluray3d/b/ref=sd_allcat_blu/186-7411295-4727002?ie=UTF8&node=2901953011", "description_title": "More About Blu-ray at Amazon Movies & TV", "keyword_count": {"blu ray": 6, "movies": 4, "amazon": 1, "movies tv": 2}, "description_wc": 111, "description_text": "The Amazon.com Movies & TV Blu-ray Store is your one-stop shop for everything Blu-ray. Browse best sellers, today\u2019s deals, top new and upcoming releases, hit movies, and more. Find titles to take advantage of everything your Blu-ray player offers: high-definition 1080p video, multi-channel surround sound, extra features with Bonus View or online with BD Live, or immersive 3D Blu-ray titles. Take a look at customer Blu-ray reviews of movies, TV shows, documentaries, and other favorites, from the Star Wars series to Avatar. Whether you\u2019re shopping for a gift or are an avid collector, you\u2019ll find the best Blu-ray movies here.", "parent_text": "Movies, Music, Games", "keyword_density": {"blu ray": "10.8", "movies": "3.6", "amazon": "0.9", "movies tv": "3.6"}, "department_id": 63},
